  "text": "The eGFR was calculated by the Modification of Diet in Renal Disease (MDRD) formula [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] accounting for ethnicity based upon the pre-operative, fourth post-operative day serum creatinine and peak serum creatinine within 30 days of surgery. We calculated the eGFR pre-operatively and on the fourth post-operative day, as by this stage we assumed that acute volume and haemodynamic changes associated with surgery would be resolved.",
